comments: Martin (IND) splits his feet at the start of his dribble.
Sabonis (IND) makes marginal contact with Beal's (WAS) leg at the start of his drive and does not affect his SQBR.
McDermott (IND) makes marginal contact to Beal's (WAS) body during his shooting motion on the driving shot attempt.
McDermott (IND) slightly extends his arm into Bertans' (WAS) body off-ball and does not affect his ability to defend.
McDermott (IND) makes marginal contact to Beal's (WAS) body during his shooting motion on the driving shot attempt.
Westbrook (WAS) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by LeVert (IND) and the contact is marginal.
Sabonis (IND) dislodges Gafford (WAS) from his legally obtained position during the rebound.
Gafford (WAS) briefly grasps Sabonis' (IND) arm and does not affect his FOM during the rebound.
Sabonis (IND) makes slight contact with Hachimura's (WAS) arm and does not affect his control of the ball.
LeVert (IND) makes marginal contact to Westbrook's (WAS) body during his shooting motion on the driving shot attempt.
Gafford (WAS) makes marginal contact to LeVert's (IND) body during his shooting motion on the driving shot attempt.
LeVert (IND) makes incidental contact to Bertans' (WAS) arm after the release of his jump shot attempt.
Neto (IND) cleanly deflects the loose ball from Sumner (IND) during the rebound.
Westbrook (WAS) extends his arm into Sabonis' (IND) body and dislodges him from his legal guarding position prior to the start of his upward shooting motion.
Bertans (WAS) jumps toward Sabonis (IND) and marginal contact occurs as he makes the pass.
Sabonis (IND) makes marginal contact with Westbrook's (WAS) arm during his drive and does not affect his SQBR.
Sabonis (IND) extends his forearm and makes contact with Westbrook's (WAS) body that affects his driving shot attempt.
Gafford (WAS) dislodges Sabonis (IND) from his rebounding position prior to any arm contact by Sabonis.  The foul should have been called on Gafford.
Holiday (IND) cleanly blocks Westbrook (WAS) during his driving shot attempt.
Gafford (WAS) cleanly deflects the loose ball from Sabonis (IND) during the rebound.
LeVert (IND) jumps from point A to point B and makes contact with Westbrook (WAS) that affects his jump shot attempt.
Westbrook (WAS) cleanly blocks LeVert (IND) during his jump shot attempt.
